column7: is your employer primarily a tech company/organization?
column8: is your primary role within your company related to tech/it?

column10: do you know the options for mental health care available under your employer-provided health coverage?
column11: has your employer ever formally discussed mental health (for example, as part of a wellness campaign or other official communication)?
column12: does your employer offer resources to learn more about mental health disorders and options for seeking help?

column32: would you be willing to bring up a physical health issue with a potential employer in an interview?
column33: would you bring up your mental health with a potential employer in an interview?
